---
title: Crispy Chicken Schnitzel with Garlic-Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Buttery Zucchini
description: Crispy chicken schnitzel, roasted sweet potatoes and buttery zucchini come together in this classic dinner. Our little twist? Tzatziki as a tasty dipper!
